# CI Gates

## Post-Push Poll (required)

After push to `main` or before release sign-off:

```bash
bash scripts/check-github-ci.sh HEAD --wait 300
```

Primary workflow: `.github/workflows/android-ci.yml`

## Gate Order (local — Android)

1. `bash scripts/validate-bootstrap.sh --quick`
2. `./gradlew lint test assembleDebug`
3. `bash scripts/feature-gate.sh --stack android`
4. `bash scripts/watch-agent-gates.sh --once --autofix --step <label>`
5. Milestone: `bash scripts/smoke/m{N}_smoke.sh` → record in `docs/GATES.md`

**Autonomous rule:** On gate failure, agent auto-fixes from JSON output within feature scope; re-run until pass or 3-strike. Push still requires human approval.

## Do Not Mark Complete

- BUILD_PLAN `[AUTO]` items while CI / Security Scan / CodeQL red
- Sprint sign-off without `scripts/pre-release-gate.sh` on template releases
